# manager-workspace/.gitignore
#
# This is a PRIVATE workspace. It holds meeting transcripts, political-risk notes
# and other sensitive managerial knowledge that must never leak into a team repo.
# Keep this repo private at the host (GitHub private / local-only).
#
# Ignore OS / editor noise:
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# Ignore anything explicitly marked secret:
*.secret
secrets/

# NOTE: sources/, contexts/, projects/ and people/ ARE tracked — they are the
# workspace's value. Do not ignore them.
